    "question_id" : 5920135,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You want the value set, not the key set:</p>\n\n<pre><code>for (TypeValue name: this.example.values()) {\n        System.out.println(name);\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The code you give wouldn't even compile, which may be worth mentioning in future questions - \"doesn't seem to work\" is a bit vague!</p>\n"
  }, {
