    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Assuming you have a <code>Map&lt;KeyType, ValueType&gt;</code>, you can print it like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>for (Map.Entry&lt;KeyType, ValueType&gt; entry : map.entrySet()) {\n    System.out.println(entry.getKey()+\" : \"+entry.getValue());\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
