    "body" : "<p>I did it using String map (if you're working with String Map).</p>\n\n<pre><code>for (Object obj : dados.entrySet()) {\n    Map.Entry&lt;String, String&gt; entry = (Map.Entry) obj;\n    System.out.print(\"Key: \" + entry.getKey());\n    System.out.println(\", Value: \" + entry.getValue());\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
