    "body" : "<p>Worth mentioning Java 8 approach, using <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/function/BiConsumer.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>BiConsumer</code></a> and lambda functions:</p>\n\n<pre><code>BiConsumer&lt;TypeKey, TypeValue&gt; consumer = (o1, o2) -&gt; \n           System.out.println(o1 + \", \" + o2);\n\nexample.forEach(consumer);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Assuming that you've overridden <code>toString</code> method of the two types if needed.</p>\n"
